# Library source conventions

## Strategy (`src/strategy/`)

- Implement `IStrategy`: `eventEmitter`, `onAdd`, `onClear`, `sendAll`, `destroy`
- Emit `"send"` on `eventEmitter` when the store should flush to the service
- `OnRequestStrategy`: only sends on `sendAll()`; `InstantStrategy` sends on every `onAdd`

## Service (`src/service/`)

- Extend `BaseRemoteService` for HTTP backends; override `preparePayload`, `serializer`, or `getHeaders` when the endpoint format differs
- `sendAllLogs` merges each log with `defaultLogConfig`, then calls `http.request` (axios wrapper in `src/util/http.ts`)

## LogStore

- Optional `transformations` with `TransformationEnum.RAPID_FIRE_GROUPING` — uses lodash `throttle` and `LogUtils.getLogIdByFields`
- `getAll()` flushes pending group counters before returning a copy

## Style

- Default-export classes; strict TypeScript; ES2015 target — no DOM/Node-only APIs in shared paths without guards
- Call `destroy()` to remove listeners and cancel throttles/timers
